OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FA project backed by Google's parent
OL,7,Fcompany, Alphabet, wants to release 32
OL,8,Fmillion mosquitoes in two US states.
OL,10,FDebug, a Google initiative, is seeking
OL,11,Fthe approval of the US government to
OL,12,Frelease male mosquitoes in California
OL,13,Fand Florida in a bid to decrease the
OL,14,Fnumber of 'bad' disease-spreading bugs.
OL,16,FThe plan is not without its critics,
OL,17,Fespecially residents who fear a plague
OL,18,Fof mosquitoes.
OL,20,FSo, why is Google backing this
OL,21,Fproject, and how will it work?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
