OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FWhat is the idea behind the project
OL,7,Fand how is Google involved?
OL,9,FThe Debug project wants to rear and
OL,10,Frelease male mosquitoes, which can't
OL,11,Fbite or spread disease and that carry
OL,12,Fa naturally occurring bacteria called
OL,13,FWolbachia.
OL,15,FThis makes them unable to have
OL,16,Foffspring with wild female mosquitoes,
OL,17,Fso these bugs will stop bad ones from
OL,18,Freproducing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FWhen these infected males mate with
OL,7,Fwild females, the females still lay
OL,8,Feggs, but the eggs do not develop or
OL,9,Fhatch, gradually reducing the number
OL,10,Fof disease-spreading mosquitoes in
OL,11,Faffected areas over time.
OL,13,FVerily, a life sciences company owned
OL,14,Fby Alphabet, launched the "Debug
OL,15,FProject" in 2016, with new approaches
OL,16,Fto automate the process of rearing
OL,17,Fmillions of mosquitoes, separate males
OL,18,Ffrom females and release Debug's good
OL,19,Fmosquitoes in the right place in the
OL,20,Fright numbers.
OL,26,@vD@[OUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
