PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FThe US Centres for Disease Control and
OL,7,FPrevention says mosquitoes kill more
OL,8,Fpeople than all other animals combined.
OL,10,FOne species, Aedes aegypti, carries
OL,11,Fdeadly diseases such as dengue, Zika,
OL,12,Fyellow fever, and chikungunya.
OL,14,FDebug's approach focuses on the 'bad
OL,15,Fbugs' - female Aedes aegypti - by
OL,16,Fusing 'good bugs' - male mosquitoes -
OL,17,Fcarrying a bacterium called Wolbachia,
OL,18,Fwhich causes eggs laid by females to
OL,19,Ffail, gradually shrinking the
OL,20,Fpopulation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
