PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FIs anyone against it?
OL,8,FYes. The plan has drawn criticism
OL,9,Fonline and from some politicians, with
OL,10,Fconcerns about it meddling with nature
OL,11,Fand possibly having unintended
OL,12,Fconsequences.
OL,14,FCritics question whether removing a
OL,15,Fspecies could affect ecosystems, even
OL,16,Fthough project scientists argue Aedes
OL,17,Faegypti is an invasive species with a
OL,18,Flimited ecological role in food chains.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
