OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,F"Why does Google have 32 million
OL,7,Fmosquitoes? Have we not learned our
OL,8,Flesson with Kudzu, Sparrows, Black
OL,9,FBirds, Asian Carp? Should I go on?"
OL,10,FTennessee Republican Representative
OL,11,FTim Burchett said on social media.
OL,13,F"Don't mess with the balance of
OL,14,Fnature."
OL,16,FWhat do supporters say?
OL,26,@qD@cO]uD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
