CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FVerily's project website says the
OL,7,Fgeneral scientific consensus is that
OL,8,Fremoving the targeted mosquitoes from
OL,9,Furban areas would have little
OL,10,Fecological impact, as they are not
OL,11,Fconsidered to be a major food source
OL,12,Ffor other animals.
