CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FThe Debug team says it is working with
OL,7,Fcommunities and regulators to ensure
OL,8,Fthe safety and acceptability of its
OL,9,Ffield trials and any future releases.
OL,11,FOther supporters also point to
OL,12,Fprevious trials in countries such as
OL,13,Fthe US, Singapore and Australia, where
OL,14,Fsimilar approaches have been used
OL,15,Fsuccessfully.
OL,17,FHow long will the project take?
OL,19,FThere is currently no fixed timeline
OL,20,Ffor when the mosquito releases could
OL,21,Fbegin.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
