OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780499462
OL,3,CWhy does Google want to release more
OL,4,Cthan 30 million mosquitoes in the US?
OL,6,FResearchers say that even after adult
OL,7,Fmosquitoes are reduced, eggs can
OL,8,Fremain dormant in the environment for
OL,9,Fmonths, meaning the programme would
OL,10,Fneed ongoing treatment in an area over
OL,11,Fan extended period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
